metadata.name: Larva Apes Hidden
metadata.description:
Larva Apes are a merge between the CryptoPunks, Bored Ape Yacht Club and a splash of Larva Lads. A tribute to the most iconic NFTs in history. 

These randomly generated creatures come with 2 Larva Apes. Your first Larva ape is equipped purely for design and hysterical memes. Your second Larva Ape will have metadata and are fully on-chain ERC721 NFTs. They are equipped metaverse ready, will be able to be used as avatars in future games and more.
